Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.54,0:01:45.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咪  我吃饱了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.89,0:01:54.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大石先生  好迟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.00,0:01:58.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且约好的时间早就过了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.14,0:02:01.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巡警先生从中午就一直守在外面
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.40,0:02:05.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有人来换班也真可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.22,0:02:08.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是出什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.26,0:02:10.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我觉得如果是大石先生的话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.33,0:02:13.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该不会有什么问题
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.79,0:02:18.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「黄莺」呼叫本部
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.30,0:02:21.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,射杀两名人员的尸体处理完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.28,0:02:24.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总部收到  加快作业
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.79,0:02:30.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到情报  接班的警察即将赶到目标家中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.69,0:02:33.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,计划不会有更改
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.47,0:02:34.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.65,0:02:36.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除掉刑警也没关系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.23,0:02:37.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.18,0:02:42.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚  古手神社里面的所有人都会失踪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.97,0:02:44.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成为「鬼隐」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.38,0:02:47.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大石先生出什么事情了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.45,0:02:48.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.60,0:02:51.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只听说途中和警局联络过一次
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.89,0:02:55.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  你们也回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.11,0:02:56.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.31,0:02:59.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后还有我们在  不要紧的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.73,0:03:01.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再不回家  你们家人会担心的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.54,0:03:19.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家说明天还回来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.24,0:03:23.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么明天就要准备好些点心才行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.31,0:03:25.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是能留下吃晚饭的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.55,0:03:28.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要便食  能做些菜的话就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.24,0:03:29.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.35,0:03:31.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能到来还不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.42,0:03:35.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直要心怀不安来度过这一夜么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.96,0:03:37.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨花？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.20,0:03:39.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.17,0:03:41.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就不要换睡衣了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.98,0:03:44.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直接穿外衣睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.48,0:03:47.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出什么事的话也能立刻行动对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.61,0:03:48.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙都子…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.09,0:03:50.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以防万一啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.09,0:03:56.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧  神社周围设下的陷阱是通常的三倍哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.68,0:04:02.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  不确定的未来对现在的我来说才正是希望
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.27,0:04:11.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨花
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.74,0:04:12.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.69,0:04:17.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？你肚子饿了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.31,0:04:21.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上就到时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.65,0:04:29.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以  不可以被这样的感情淹没
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.02,0:04:33.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要相信  要相信  要相信…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.88,0:04:38.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧  羽入
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.84,0:04:40.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会反抗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.59,0:04:42.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算明天就会被杀害
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.88,0:04:46.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也要反抗这今夜将被杀害的命运！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.97,0:04:51.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.61,0:05:02.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是「凤4」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.41,0:05:04.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包含目标在内两人逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.64,0:05:06.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们追
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.91,0:05:10.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脚底上有陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.12,0:05:15.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「凤6」「凤7」  目标逃往后山了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.20,0:05:17.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点抓住他们！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.20,0:05:17.18,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（"他"没错）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.61,0:05:19.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「凤6」明白
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.77,0:05:25.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才那声音是什么？枪击吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.33,0:05:28.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  是鞭炮  可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.88,0:05:33.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是沙都子吧  真行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.63,0:05:34.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真丢脸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.23,0:05:36.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注意监视周围情况
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.91,0:05:38.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让她们逃入民居就麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.75,0:05:41.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「凤9」发现目标
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.27,0:05:44.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在后山的北面  请求支援
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.87,0:05:46.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她们两个方向感很好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.19,0:05:49.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不快点抓住她们就真的会追丢的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.59,0:05:52.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他  他们是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.64,0:05:54.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是梨花你说的「东京」吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.89,0:05:55.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.99,0:05:57.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说了  快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.51,0:05:59.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被抓住的话  可是会被杀的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.12,0:06:03.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们要去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.79,0:06:04.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魅的家里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.05,0:06:06.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地下的秘密房间的话很安全
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.18,0:06:08.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也能和外部进行联络
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.62,0:06:10.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨花！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.27,0:06:14.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙都子  快跑！连你也会被杀的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.50,0:06:19.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点  梨花
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.55,0:06:21.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢  沙都子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.01,0:06:26.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那衣服  果然黑幕是鹰野吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.88,0:06:29.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要得知犯人是鹰野的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.18,0:06:32.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算在这里被杀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.45,0:06:34.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下一个世界也一定会有办法的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.18,0:06:38.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能死  不将这记忆继承下来的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.37,0:06:41.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快跑  梨花！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.56,0:06:42.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙都子！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.59,0:06:44.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里交给我  你快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.30,0:06:47.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是我在这里逃跑的话  沙都子她就…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.01,0:06:49.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这绝对不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.59,0:06:52.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拼上这条命也不会让沙都子被杀的！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.56,0:06:55.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  我不会活下去的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.21,0:06:58.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就会失去好不容易得来的事实
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.85,0:07:01.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这记忆不继承下去的话一切都是无用功了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.25,0:07:04.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抛弃沙都子也要活下去…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.32,0:07:08.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我办不到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.95,0:07:11.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也真是够蠢了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.73,0:07:16.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了你们的真面目还不选择逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.99,0:07:19.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  我不会逃避的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.88,0:07:22.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命运是足以打破的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.75,0:07:24.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人这样告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.78,0:07:31.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圭一！蕾娜！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.86,0:07:35.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魅音  诗音！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.68,0:07:36.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们两个不要紧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.28,0:07:38.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会来这里？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.61,0:07:41.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾娜她说有不好的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.05,0:07:45.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像被什么人盯着的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.36,0:07:47.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我感觉到气息了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.81,0:07:51.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亏你能察觉到  不愧是蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.83,0:07:55.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我们就拿着能当作武器的东西又回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.48,0:08:00.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真想不到会在这里被大家所救
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.91,0:08:01.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真吓死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.35,0:08:04.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回来的时候巡警都倒下了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.25,0:08:06.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.19,0:08:11.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们打算逃进魅音的家里  地下那里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.29,0:08:13.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祭具殿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.06,0:08:18.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也赞成  那里面有好几条秘密通道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.73,0:08:21.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么赶快  追兵很快就会来的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.74,0:08:25.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点回话！「凤6」「凤9」怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.18,0:08:29.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,几个小鬼就被搞成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.34,0:08:32.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可不是单纯的小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.91,0:08:37.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其中可是有被称作「御社神转世」的孩子在
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.69,0:08:38.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三佐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.25,0:08:44.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  真正的御社神  才即将要现世呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.18,0:09:01.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上到了  加油
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.87,0:09:02.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿圭  你看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.06,0:09:05.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.24,0:09:09.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办  走这条路的话会被追上的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.21,0:09:12.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要揍趴他们  开一条路出来么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.50,0:09:15.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊  顺利的话车也能抢到手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.27,0:09:17.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驾驶就交给我了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.10,0:09:20.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魅  你有驾照吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.72,0:09:24.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在是非常时期  不要在意细节
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.36,0:09:26.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦呵呵呵呵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.40,0:09:28.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可真是好提案啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.21,0:09:31.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么决定了  我们上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.79,0:09:39.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里！抓住她！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.49,0:09:48.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解决一个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.75,0:09:54.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好注意背后啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.35,0:09:56.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交给圭一君了  拜托咯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.91,0:09:59.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没杀他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.29,0:10:02.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧  是刀背
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.33,0:10:07.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种小鬼把戏
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.00,0:10:13.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是因为是小孩就小看我们那才叫人困扰呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.58,0:10:15.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是部团活动的成果呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.69,0:10:20.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.96,0:10:25.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来是收拾干净了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.28,0:10:28.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挺轻松的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.72,0:10:31.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为大家齐心协力在努力嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.61,0:10:34.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对手是6个  我们也是6个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.65,0:10:38.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想少了谁都不行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.44,0:10:44.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  大家齐心协力的话  一定会打破命运的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.17,0:10:45.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.89,0:10:56.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对手不愧是专业的  一开始那些家伙就已经察觉了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.79,0:10:59.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算什么  我们更有士气
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.43,0:11:01.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起的话  就没什么好怕的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.63,0:11:06.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羽入  你还是一如既往地死心了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.80,0:11:12.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,垂死挣扎的力量如何  你就好好看清楚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.91,0:11:19.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.09,0:11:23.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命运正在…改变！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.36,0:11:37.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圭一…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.41,0:11:41.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鹰野！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.08,0:11:45.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿圭  振作点！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.63,0:11:52.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱…抱歉…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.89,0:11:55.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要退场了…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.88,0:11:59.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们快跑…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.84,0:12:02.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要…骗人！骗人…！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.88,0:12:05.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿圭你怎么会就这么死掉…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.76,0:12:11.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.95,0:12:15.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家…快跑啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.55,0:12:19.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在只要考虑怎么活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.64,0:12:22.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留在这里不是圭一君想要的结果
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.01,0:12:29.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家  快跑啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.37,0:12:34.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们…要活下去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.12,0:12:49.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对方人越来越多了  赶快
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.57,0:12:52.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小魅？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.54,0:12:53.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我留下来当诱饵
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.36,0:12:57.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我拖延时间的时候  大家快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.67,0:12:58.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.13,0:13:00.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有争论的时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.28,0:13:03.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有保护沙都子的义务
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.95,0:13:08.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾娜  梨花就交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.98,0:13:10.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们走  梨花
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.53,0:13:12.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魅…魅！魅！！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.49,0:13:20.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是稍微休息一下  知道了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.68,0:13:23.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知…道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.78,0:13:27.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐这笨蛋…耍什么威风…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.48,0:13:30.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.20,0:13:32.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小魅
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.48,0:13:33.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐？你没事吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.14,0:13:37.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魅音…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.08,0:13:43.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思哦  她已经死了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.72,0:13:48.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小诗  他们两个就拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.63,0:13:49.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.66,0:13:50.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.57,0:13:57.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连续怪死事件全都是鹰野小姐干的好事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.68,0:14:01.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想做御社神大人的代行者吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.17,0:14:07.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不是代行者  是我降下的天罚哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.14,0:14:10.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来村中所发生的天罚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.82,0:14:12.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将是我降下的天罚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.58,0:14:15.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此之后  我将超越人类
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.73,0:14:16.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成为神
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.55,0:14:19.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成为御社神本身
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.71,0:14:22.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想是没可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.65,0:14:26.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鹰野小姐做什么  不过是小孩子扮家家酒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.07,0:14:29.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你无法成为御社神大人的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.12,0:14:32.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会成为的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.93,0:14:34.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来我就将成为…！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.44,0:14:39.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说了不行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.67,0:14:41.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要知道御社神大人是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.83,0:14:42.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.88,0:14:48.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.52,0:14:50.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我受够了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.54,0:14:53.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我受不了这样下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.42,0:14:58.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀了我…快点杀了我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.85,0:14:59.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙都子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.92,0:15:03.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以说这种话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.33,0:15:05.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诗音…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.41,0:15:08.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多一分一秒也要活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.54,0:15:09.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要活着！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.76,0:15:11.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会保护你的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.28,0:15:12.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包括悟史君的份在一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.61,0:15:14.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥的…？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.88,0:15:16.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.30,0:15:32.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  从谁开始呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.93,0:15:35.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要杀沙都子！求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.99,0:15:37.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要杀我就尽管来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.40,0:15:40.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但求你放过沙都子！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.84,0:15:45.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呵呵呵  我会考虑一下的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.36,0:15:53.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得她来求我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.97,0:15:56.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说怎么办呢  沙都子妹妹？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.80,0:15:59.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那来回答问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.99,0:16:05.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西兰花和花椰菜  哪个是绿色的？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.33,0:16:09.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花…西兰花…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.39,0:16:12.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正确
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.43,0:16:24.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是要杀死我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.34,0:16:26.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  当然要杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.29,0:16:30.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女王感染者的尸体是作战的关键
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.04,0:16:36.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你将成为远离此地的「东京」的丑恶政治斗争的道具
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.18,0:16:41.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同时  也将成为鬼之渊村传说的终结
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.36,0:16:45.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确是鹰野能想出来的事情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.28,0:16:49.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚安  梨花
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.82,0:16:52.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢着
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.13,0:16:55.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  求饶吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.62,0:17:00.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  要杀我的话  不要让我睡着再下手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.18,0:17:02.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.04,0:17:04.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想走得轻松点么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.26,0:17:08.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很疼哦  活生生把你的肚子刨开
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.21,0:17:11.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了牢记
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.17,0:17:16.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会把你将我刨腹的事实深深印在我的灵魂上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.37,0:17:23.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了在下一次遇见你的时候  能够回想起你是我的敌人！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.51,0:17:31.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨花
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.74,0:17:34.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又…又失败了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.67,0:17:37.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系  羽入
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.88,0:17:41.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们竭尽全力了  只差一步了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.00,0:17:43.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨花
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.51,0:17:46.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我是不会就此屈服的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.78,0:17:49.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算这记忆不会继承
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.64,0:17:53.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算下个雏见泽只需数日便会结束
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.50,0:17:57.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也要不择手段的活着活着活下去！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.71,0:18:00.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  下次一定要…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.56,0:18:10.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我绝不会忘记这次死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.01,0:18:15.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不会忘记
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.65,0:18:18.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算梨花忘记了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.19,0:18:21.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也一定会告诉你的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.20,0:18:27.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想和大家一起活在一个快乐的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.99,0:18:36.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.39,0:18:39.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.76,0:18:42.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差一点就可以打破命运了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.27,0:18:47.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家齐心协力努力过了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.21,0:18:49.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.60,0:18:52.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.55,0:18:54.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  还不够
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.93,0:18:57.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果反抗命运的意识再强烈一些的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.31,0:19:00.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们都这样相信着
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.12,0:19:03.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是差了一点没有达到而已
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.07,0:19:06.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  梨花
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.00,0:19:09.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没能拯救你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.08,0:19:12.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.58,0:19:14.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢大家
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.00,0:19:16.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的谢谢大家了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.60,0:19:31.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来这次也只能放弃了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.26,0:19:36.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算大家齐心协力  也没能打破命运
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.22,0:19:37.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.40,0:19:43.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇迹没有发生的理由  蕾娜是明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.55,0:19:47.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的相信了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.25,0:19:50.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呜  啊呜啊呜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.38,0:19:53.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是无能为力的弱小存在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.94,0:19:58.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只凭我这样只能看的人来相信也不会…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.45,0:19:59.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇迹会发生的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.51,0:20:06.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  我们再加上你的话  我想奇迹一定会发生的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.07,0:20:10.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你需要与命运对抗的勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.32,0:20:13.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你是我们的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.10,0:20:14.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们走
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.50,0:20:16.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.46,0:20:17.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.44,0:20:28.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.44,0:20:30.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向我们的下一个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.55,0:20:39.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两千人！是两千人啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.08,0:20:45.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先应该制裁想出这烂点子的「东京」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.66,0:20:50.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雏见泽症候群就同我说的一样是非常危险的病症
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.69,0:20:53.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果泄露的话损害就不只是两千人这么多了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.74,0:20:56.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须实施必要的处理
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.33,0:21:00.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能把损害减少到最小吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.87,0:21:03.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一点我保证
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.35,0:21:14.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始灭菌
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.82,0:21:34.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一小队报告本部
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.39,0:21:35.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,营林所的灭菌终了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.30,0:21:37.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,射杀逃脱者4名
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.16,0:21:40.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二小队报告本部
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.72,0:21:43.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,约十名逃脱者进入山林
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.47,0:21:44.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在扫荡中
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.79,0:21:52.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无罚无神  因罚生惧  有惧乃敬
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.29,0:21:55.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此刻即是神明降临之际
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.91,0:21:58.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本人亦为御社之神！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.93,0:23:45.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前我就想问了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.63,0:23:46.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.91,0:23:50.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羽入你说的「啊呜啊呜」是什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.26,0:23:53.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那个是单纯的意识表现
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.64,0:23:55.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有疑问的时候会出现
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.96,0:23:56.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.85,0:24:01.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把「在情况不妙的时候让周遭知道我真的很难过」
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.19,0:24:04.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「希望不要再让我这么难过了的说」
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.61,0:24:08.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的感情用可爱形式表现出来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.54,0:24:10.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…啊呜啊呜
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.96,0:24:12.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来是被我说中了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.48,0:24:14.11,yokoku,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.25,0:24:16.20,yokoku,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祭{\fnDFGHSMincho-W9\fs23\1c&H0000ff&}囃{\r}篇  其一
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.56,0:24:17.14,yokoku,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三四
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.44,0:24:19.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呜  啊呜
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.30,0:24:21.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对的说  不对的说
